These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, security-guard, librarian
1. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
2. the entrepreneur is not to the left of the security-guard##8
3. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Job   | librarian | security-guard | entrepreneur |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, dunhill, chaman
1. the chaman-smoker is not to the left of the dannemann-smoker##8
2. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Cigar   | dannemann | chaman | dunhill |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, dubstep, reggae
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of funk is not to the right of the fan of reggae##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | funk | reggae |

 #################################

 
